data.description: Welcome Home!  This tri-level makes you feel at home once you walk in the door.  The living room and kitchen are full of natural light and have nice black appliances.  Go upstairs to the three bedrooms with more natural light and wood flooring.  For your quiet evenings go downstairs to the nice second living area and step out the sliding door to your backyard retreat.  Plus, this home offers a 569 sq foot basement perfect for a man cave, crafters area or extra storage.  The front yard has great curb appeal, and the back yard is ready for you to relax and entertain family and friends.  This home is waiting for you to move right in and enjoy!
